         <abstract>
            <p>We analyze the approximation properties of some interpolation operators and some $L^2_\omega$-orthogonal projection operators related to systems of polynomials which are orthonormal with respect to a weight function $\omega(x_1,\ldots, x_d), d \geqslant 1$. The error estimates for the Legendre system and the Chebyshev system of the first kind are given in the norms of the Sobolev spaces $H^s_\omega$. These results are useful in the numerical analysis of the approximation of partial differential equations by spectral methods.</p>
          </abstract>
